  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个SJF非抢占式调度的甘特图，时间范围是0到15秒，展示CPU和I/O两个section。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section CPU",
        "section I/O",
        "0 15s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，SJF非抢占式意味着一旦进程开始执行就不会被中断。我需要确认一下，这个图要展示的是Parte 1对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "preemptive",
        "parte"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是Parte 1。先画CPU部分，P1从0秒开始，执行到5秒结束，这是第一个任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "0 5",
        "cpu1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，P1(0-5)已经加到CPU section了，标记为active状态。接下来P1结束后会进入I/O吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P1_IO",
        "active",
        "5 7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，P1在5秒结束后立即进入I/O，持续到7秒。同时CPU在5秒时要调度下一个最短作业。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1_IO",
        "P4",
        "5 7",
        "cpu2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "下一个最短作业是P4对吗？它的CPU burst时间是2秒，从5到7。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "5 7",
        "cpu2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，P4执行到7秒结束，然后它也要进I/O。这时候CPU空闲出来，要调度P2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "P4_IO",
        "P2",
        "7 10"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P4(5-7)已添加，P4_IO(7-10)也放到I/O section了。现在加P2到CPU，7到10秒对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4_IO",
        "P2",
        "7 10",
        "cpu3",
        "io2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P2执行3秒。10秒时P2结束，同时P1的I/O也刚好在7秒结束，但P2的I/O要更晚开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2",
        "P2_IO",
        "P1_IO",
        "10 11"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我理一下：10秒时P2结束CPU执行，进入I/O；同时P3作为剩余最短作业进入CPU。P2的I/O只持续1秒，到11秒？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2_IO",
        "P3",
        "10 11",
        "10 14",
        "cpu4",
        "io3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。P3的CPU burst最长，从10执行到14秒。然后14秒时P4的I/O也结束了，要回来完成最后1秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3",
        "10 14",
        "P4",
        "P4_IO",
        "14 15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P3(10-14)已添加。P4在14秒回来，执行到15秒结束。这样所有进程都在15秒内完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3",
        "P4",
        "14 15",
        "cpu4",
        "cpu5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，P4回来的这个片段，时间轴上应该是14到15，和P3结束无缝衔接对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "14 15",
        "P3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，P3在14结束，P4在14开始，没有间隙。现在I/O部分需要标记为crit状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "14 15",
        "crit"
